beer.beer_description:
When two good brewers come together, what do they come up with?           

A Dark Rye Saison of course. Fermented with Sailors Grave in-house saison yeast strain   and brewed with Pink Peppercorn and dry-hopped with Pink Grapefruit.   It’s citrusy, spicy and refreshing. It’ll be Good Till The Grave.
